KARACHI, Aug 16 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Sunday visited the residence of renowned journalist Chand Nawab here to condole over the demise of his mother.
Expressing grief over the demise of the journalist’s mother, the president prayed for peace of the departed soul and courage to the bereaved family to bear the loss with equanimity.
